## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0864d-109"><xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> 當沒有環境交易時，可能會停止回應和<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Complete%2A>稱為和之後會回復交易。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0864d-109"><xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> may hang when there is an ambient transaction and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Complete%2A> is called and afterwards the transaction is rolled back.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0864d-110">如果<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A>會呼叫在交易回復完成前，競爭條件會存在，導致呼叫<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A>看似已停止回應。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0864d-110">If <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> is called prior to the transaction rollback completing, a race condition will exist, causing the call to <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> to hang.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0864d-111">這可以在下列虛擬程式碼範例所說明</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0864d-111">This can be illustrated by the following pseudo-code example</span></span>  
  
```  
using (TransactionScope ts = new TransactionScope())   
{  
   try  
   {  
       rc.Complete();  
      ...  
   }  
   Catch (Exception)   
   {  
      rc.Abandon()  
   }  
}  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0864d-112">這不是建議的模式使用<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0864d-112">This is not the recommended pattern for working with <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0864d-113">而是應該放 try/catch 區塊的交易範圍之外。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0864d-113">Instead the try/catch block should be placed outside of the transaction scope.</span></span>

